Erhapspay erewhay erethay areyay oremay Imeksslay, atthay isyay erewhay eshay aymay ebay iddenhay. Iyay usttray atthay ouyay ancay endfay erhay offyay andyay eachtay erhay ayay essonlay, hmyay?

Hmyay... ohyay! Iyay understandyay atthay ethay Atacombscay aymay avehay eenbay allengingchay otay ouyay, esyay? O-Ohyay...? Onay? Ellway... inyay asecay ifyay ouyay idn'tday owknay, ityay eemssay asyay oughthay ethay Atacombscay iftsshay itsyay ormfay eachyay imetay ouyay enteryay. Ethay ortalpay eadinglay intoyay emthay isyay orruptedcay, alwaysyay angingchay atwhay appenshay ithinway. Iyay owknay ou'reyay upyay otay ethay asktay, ittlelay oneyay... Eepsway outyay ethay evilyay atthay esidesray insideyay ethay Atacombscay, omfray ethay artstay otay ethay endyay. Eturnray otay emay onceyay ouyay avehay oneday isthay allengechay ormallynay... andyay ofyay oursecay, easeplay ebay afesay.

Ouryay oulsay isyay asyay ongstray asyay everyay, ittlelay oneyay. Whyyay on'tday eway tryyay omethingsay ayay ittlelay oremay... ellway, aringday? Erethay isyay ayay allsmay assagepay uckedtay awayyay ithinway ethay Outeryay Anctumsay, armingsway ithway awfulyay eaturescray ownknay asyay Ekboarsmay. Eythay andbray evastatingday eaponsway onyay eirthay eadshay, ookinglay otay ickpay ayay ightfay ithway anyoneyay owhay eadstray onyay eirthay urftay... Ifyay ouyay ouldway, isplayday ouryay illskay byyay ayingslay 20 Ekboarsmay andyay athergay 15 ofyay eirthay earsspay. Eturnray otay emay enwhay ouyay avehay...

Ouyay eemsay otay ebay usingyay ouryay engthstray atherray ellway, ostlay oneyay. <color=yellow>Aketay isthay ollscray.</color> <color=cyan>Eadingray ityay illway allowyay ouyay otay olsterbay ouryay owerpay usingyay one-handedyay eleemay eaponsway.</color> Ocusfay ellway, andyay ouyay illway ebay ableyay otay argechay attackyay andyay umpjay attackyay againstyay ouryay enemiesyay ithway evastatingday orcefay.\n \n<color=yellow>Omecay ackbay otay emay anytimeyay ifyay ouyay econsiderray ouryay oicechay. Iyay illway ovidepray asyay anymay ollsscray asyay ouyay eednay. Ememberray atthay ouryay ollscray illway anishvay ifyay ouyay oselay ityay.</color>

<color=cyan>Ityay akestay immenseyay engthstray otay useyay eavyhay eaponsway, ostlay oneyay.</color> Iyay eesay atthay ouyay avehay otentialpay inyay usingyay emthay. <color=yellow>Ifyay ouyay inkthay ouyay ancay andlehay isthay urdenbay ofyay arway, aketay isthay ollscray.</color> <color=cyan>Eadingray ityay illway eachtay ouyay atwhay erethay isyay otay owknay inyay ashingsmay ouryay oesfay intoyay oodyblay iecespay.</color>\n \n<color=yellow>Omecay ackbay otay emay anytimeyay ifyay ouyay econsiderray ouryay oicechay. Iyay illway ovidepray asyay anymay ollsscray asyay ouyay eednay. Ememberray atthay ouryay ollscray illway anishvay ifyay ouyay oselay ityay.</color>

Olearmspay ingbray emay ackbay otay ayay ostalgicnay imetay ofyay ainingtray. Uchmay ikelay otheryay eleemay eaponsway, <color=cyan>eythay areyay iablevay oolstay ofyay arway.</color> Iyay eesay ayay arkspay inyay ouryay eyeyay, ostlay oneyay. <color=yellow>Aketay isthay ollscray, asyay ityay illway eachtay ouyay otay applyyay igherhay illskay otay ouryay useyay ofyay olearmspay.</color>\n \n<color=yellow>Omecay ackbay otay emay anytimeyay ifyay ouyay econsiderray ouryay oicechay. Iyay illway ovidepray asyay anymay ollsscray asyay ouyay eednay. Ememberray atthay ouryay ollscray illway anishvay ifyay ouyay oselay ityay.</color>

Ethay imetay ashay omecay otay akemay ethay ultimateyay ecisionday, ostlay oneyay. Iyay eesay atthay ethay engthstray andyay illskay ouyay avehay atheredgay ashay eenbay oremay anthay ufficentsay <color=cyan>otay ingbray orthfay ouryay uetray olorscay ofyay ecomingbay ayay Ighterfay.</color>
 
Ecomingbay ayay Ighterfay illway akemay ouyay ayay ivinglay eatthray againstyay ethay evilyay onstrositiesmay atthay oatcay isthay orldway. <color=yellow>Aketay isthay ometay.</color> Onceyay eadray, ouyay illway oinjay emay inyay ouryay effortyay otay ivideday ethay arknessday.
 
<color=yellow>Ifyay ouyay appenhay otay oselay ouryay ometay undecidedyay, eturnray otay emay. Iyay ancay ovidepray asyay anymay asyay ouyay eednay.</color> <color=cyan>Eepkay inyay indmay, eadingray isthay ometay isyay irreversibleyay.</color>

Ethay imetay isyay ownay, ostlay oneyay. <color=cyan>Ethay Anctumsay Atacombscay inallyfay uncoveredyay itsyay uetray elfsay, andyay ethay omentmay otay ikestray erewhay ethay undeadyay eastlay expectyay ityay isyay erehay.</color> Asyay oolishfay andyay aimlessyay asyay eythay areyay, ethay undeadyay inyay isthay incantationyay areyay uthlessray inyay eirthay owerpay.
 
Esethay onstrositiesmay ustmay ebay oppedstay eforebay eythay aimyay otay urtherfay orruptcay ouryay andlay. <color=yellow>Ayslay 25 Iasmamay, 15 Ellsludgehay, andyay 30 Oltergeistspay. Ouyay ancay indfay emthay inyay ethay ardesthay Anctumsay Atacombscay.</color> Etlay ethay undeadyay uffersay ouryay athwray, onay urvivorssay.

<color=cyan>Ethay Escentcray Ovegray isyay ayay alicemay otay isthay orldway.</color> Ethay eaturescray atthay armsway ithinway ethay ovegray areyay otnay upyay otay uffsnay otay ouryay andardsstay, ostlay oneyay. Ilencesay emthay, andyay utpay eirthay orruptedcay indsmay otay estray.
 
<color=yellow>Estroyday 30 Eadwoodsday, 25 Arbunclescay, 10 Edray andyay Ueblay Inchroomsmay, andyay 15 Onolithsmay.</color> Eturnray otay emay atyay onceyay enwhay ouryay asktay isyay ompletedcay.

Ethay Ageboarsray inyay Uultay Alleyvay areyay owardscay. Otay inkthay eythay ancay andstay ayay ancechay againstyay usyay isyay aughablelay.
 
<color=cyan>Eepday inyay ethay Alleyvay isyay ayay empletay, overrunyay ithway ethay amnday ingsthay.</color> Esethay eviousday oarsbay ereway onstructedcay byyay anyay ominousyay evilyay eingbay atthay ashay onay emorseray orfay isthay orldway. Eway illway iscussday ofyay erhay enwhay ouryay imetay isyay eadyray, ostlay oneyay. Orfay ownay, eway ustmay ocusfay onyay atwhay ouyay ancay andlehay.
 
<color=yellow>Ayslay 20 Ageboarsray. Eythay areyay iddenhay ithinway ethay empletay Iyay avehay okenspay ofyay, inyay Uultay Alleyvay.</color> Ebay advisedyay atthay oinggay eepday inyay ethay empletay ancay etgay ouyay illedkay ifyay ou'reyay otnay arefulcay.

Iyay eesay atthay ouyay avehay alignedyay ourselfyay ellway againstyay ethay oesfay inyay Escentcray Eepkay. Oodgay orkway, ostlay oneyay. <color=cyan>Ityay isyay imetay ownay otay aketay ayay epstay urtherfay eyondbay ethay Eepkay, otay ethay Escentcray Ovegray.</color> Atwhay ouyay illway itnessway erethay isyay ayay oulfay armsway ofyay arkday agicsmay, ithway anymay ofyay ouryay allenfay indkay omfray agesyay astpay embracingyay ethay orruptioncay.
 
Erethay areyay otway othersbray, omwhay Iyay asway onceyay amiliarfay ithway. Eythay areyay ownay ickedway Arbunclescay, eetingmay ethay amesay atefay ethay othersyay avehay. <color=cyan>Ethay othersbray eatedcray ayay olemgay, oneyay atthay isyay apablecay ofyay earingtay ethay orldway asunderyay.</color> Eway ustmay utpay anyay endyay otay eirthay owardicecay. <color=yellow>Estroyday ethay Olossuscay, enthay eturnray otay emay.</color>
 
<color=yellow>Ifyay ouyay aven'thay oneday osay, eakspay otay Angelayay. Eshay ancay uidegay ouyay otay ethay Escentcray Ovegray.</color>

<color=cyan>Ethay Anctumsay Atacombscay isyay ayay evernay endingyay ellscapehay, ivendray inyay ayay oalgay otay ingbray Anctumsay otay itsyay eesknay.</color> Ortunatelyfay orfay usyay, ey'rethay ootay upidstay otay ealizeray owhay ey'rethay ealingday ithway. Ethay amountyay ofyay atiencepay Iyay avehay ithway esethay atheticpay eaturescray isyay unningray inthay.
 
<color=cyan>Ithway ethay ivledgepray ofyay myyay engthstray imbuedyay ithway ouryay oulsay, eway ancay akemay ethay undeadyay eamscray inyay agonyyay ogethertay.</color> <color=yellow>Ayslay 25 Oxinstay, 15 Eathgelsday, andyay 30 Eistsgay. Ouyay ancay indfay emthay inyay ethay ormalnay Anctumsay Atacombscay.</color> Isthay ouldshay ebay ayay umouroushay eminderray orfay ethay undeadyay otay owknay exactlyyay owhay ontrolscay isthay andlay.

Istenlay. Oday ouyay earhay ityay? Ere'sthay ayay aintfay oundsay ofyay aughterlay inyay ethay istanceday, omingcay omfray ethay Atacombscay. Ithinway ityay isyay anyay entityyay atthay isyay ethay anifestationmay atthay ontinuescay otay eanimateray ethay eadday. Isthay entityyay isyay amednay Ordlay Uulnerudazay. Ayay "Eistlordgay", oneyay ofyay ethay igherhay elitesyay inyay ethay undeadyay anksray. Ehay ustmay ebay urgedpay. Eeksay Uulnerudazay, andyay illkay imhay. Ehay isyay iddenhay ithinway ethay ediummay ayerlay ofyay ethay orruptedcay ortalpay. Urryhay, ostlay oneyay... imetay isyay ofyay ethay essenceyay. Eturnray otay emay enwhay ishay oodblay isyay inyay ouryay andshay. [Efeatday Ordlay Uulnerudazay inyay ethay (LVyay6-12) Anctumsay Atacombscay.]

Owy'knay, Iyay ouldcay useyay omethinsay' ofyay ouryay elphay, ifyay ayay on'tday indmay! <color=cyan>Ifyay ou'reyay upyay otay ityay, I'llyay etlay ouyay inyay onyay ayay ecretsay ootay-- utbay eepkay ityay onyay ethay ushhay ushhay!</color>
 
I'myay ookinlay' orfay ayay ecialspay ombinationcay ofyay ostlyghay oodsgay, <color=cyan>ethay etypay atthay ancay ebay ixedmay intoyay ayay inefay illay' owderpay atthay akesmay ouyay invisibleyay!</color> 
 
Ifyay ayay ouldcay, <color=yellow>etchfay emay omesay Ostdustsghay omfray emthay undeadyay ellasfay, andyay ayay andfulhay ofyay osethay eirdway illay' ollarscay ethay Eistsgay earway omfray ethay Atacombscay!</color>
 
Omecay ackbay enwhay ayay otgay ayay oodgay amountyay ofyay emyay', ayay earhay?

Mmm-hmyay! At'dwhay ayay inkthay ofyay atthay owderpay, unhay? Ettypray iftynay, ightray? Aysay, ifyay ayay antway ummoresay, owhay outbay' ouyay etchfay omesay Ostdustghay andyay Eistgay Ollarscay? Iyay on'tway ebay eedinnay' asyay anymay asyay eforebay. Eepinkay' indmay-- ethay Anctumsay Atacombscay isyay ethay estbay aceplay otay etgay ethay uffstay! Ingbray emay... aboutyay 20 Ostdustsghay andyay 8 Eistgay Ollarscay, andyay I'llyay ipwhay upyay othernay' atchbay orfay ayay! I'llyay akemay ityay iggerbay ootay.

Ellway ooklay atyay atthay! Aven'thay ayay eenbay usybay? I'veyay eenbay eaninmay' otay etlay ayay inyay onyay omethinsay', utbay it'llyay onlyyay ebay etweenbay usyay andyay ayay arespay ewfay! Iyay aketay ityay ayay ikelay inyshay ingsthay-- oinscay andyay ootlay? Oryay aybemay isorientingday ouryay oesfay? Iyay ancay elphay ayay ithway atthay... Elievebay ityay oryay otnay, Iyay amyay ethay Anditbay Uardiangay! Eway allyay orkway ardhay orfay ouryay usinessbay, evenyay ifyay ityay akestay ertaincay ethodsmay otay etgay ouryay ayway. Aketay isthay, andyay onsidercay oiningjay emay andyay myyay ewcray! Eepinkay' indmay ayay an'tcay evertray ouryay oicechay. Ifyay ayay oselay ouryay ometay, omecay ackbay againyay!

<color=cyan>Ou'veyay eenbay atyay ethay Escentcray Eepkay, ightray?</color> Astlay I'veyay eardhay, atthay aceplay isyay arminsway' ithway osethay illay' alitosis-riddenhay itterscray! E'reway otnay uresay atwhay otay allcay emyay', <color=cyan>osay eway ustjay allcay emyay' Outhsmay otay eepkay ingsthay implesay.</color>

<color=cyan>Ouyay ancay indfay ayay Uderay Adeblay inyay ethay Escentcray Eepkay, Imeksslay inyay ethay Effoldyay Erracetay, andyay Eathgelsday inyay ethay ormalnay Anctumsay Atacombscay!</color>

<color=cyan>Ayay everyay eesay osethay angestray Izboarsway, unhay?</color> Osethay ellasfay alwaysyay ooklay osay appyhay. Elievebay emay oughthay, ey'rethay iciousvay illay' ingsthay!

<color=cyan>Ouyay ancay indfay ayay Uderay Adeblay inyay ethay Escentcray Eepkay, Imeksslay inyay ethay Effoldyay Erracetay, andyay Eathgelsday inyay ethay ormalnay Anctumsay Atacombscay!</color>

Ayway ackbay enthay, Iyay asway alwaysyay ightinfay' otay ominateday inyay ethay usinessbay, akinmay' uresay ingsthay ereway ettingay' akentay arecay ofyay. <color=cyan>Inyay atthay imetay, Iyay usedyay ecialspay echniquestay usinyay' atarskay!</color> Arpshay illay' ingsthay, ableyay otay iceslay andyay ockknay outyay ompetitioncay inyay ayay eartbeathay!

<color=yellow>Inyay asecay ayay annaway inkthay' ityay overyay icetway, I'myay alwaysyay erehay otay ivegay anotheryay ollscray ifyay ayay eednay ityay! Ustjay owknay atthay ethay ollscray illway anishvay ifyay ayay opdray ityay, ayay earhay?</color>

<color=yellow>Inyay asecay ayay annaway inkthay' ityay overyay icetway, I'myay alwaysyay erehay otay ivegay anotheryay ollscray ifyay ayay eednay ityay! Ustjay owknay atthay ethay ollscray illway anishvay ifyay ayay opdray ityay, ayay earhay?</color>

<color=cyan>Emthay Olemsgay inyay Escentcray Eepkay areyay ongstray uggersbay!</color> Aybemay eway ancay aketay eirthay orescay andyay emsgay, akemay omethinsay' eatnay outtayay ityay! It'dyay ebay ayay estpiecechay, ayay ettypray ongstray oneyay ootay!
